          Sumamos valor a tu ecosistema ofreciendo nuevas alternativas comerciales
          y financieras que te ayudan a alcanzar tus metas con la mayor rentabilidad
          posible.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center justify-self-en absolute bottom-0 right-0 py-24 max-[1440px]:py-20 px-28">
        <a class="font-bold text-xl max-[1440px]:text-sm border-b-2 text-white" href="#"
          >Conozca más ↗</a
        >
      </div>
    </section>
    <section
      class="flex flex-row w-full h-screen overflow-hidden border-t max-[1100px]:flex-col max-[1100px]:h-full max-[1100px]:"
    >
      <section class="relative bg-[#727375] z-30">
        <div
          class="w-[35vw] p-6 max-[1100px]:py-20 pl-28 max-[1280px]:px-10  h-full top-0 left-0 flex justify-evenly max-[1100px]:justify-center max-[800px]:gap-8 max-[1100px]:w-full items-start flex-col max-[800px]:flex-col shadow-[2px_-3px_19px_0] shadow-[#adc6fb99] max-[1100px]:shadow-none max-[1100px]:flex-row max-[1100px]:items-center"
        >
          <div
            class="text-[#cce8fa] max-[1100px]:items-center max-[1100px]:pl-0 flex justify-center items-start flex-col gap-8 max-[1100px]:flex-row max-[800px]:flex-col"
          >
            <h2
              class="text-5xl max-[1680px]:text-4xl max-[1366px]:text-3xl max-[1366px]:leading-7 max-[1025px]:text-2xl max-[800px]:max-w-[500px]"
