            <p><span class="font-extrabold">SOMOS</span></p>
            <p>EMISORES</p>
            <p>PROCESADORES</p>
            <p>GENERADORES</p>
            <p>CONSULTORES</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section
        class="bg-[#041226] w-[calc(100%-30vw)] max-[1100px]:w-[100%] l-32 max-[1100px]:pl-0 max-[1100px]:py-12 max-[1100px]:h-[90vh]"
      >
        <div class="splide h-full">
          <div class="splide__track !pl-0 h-full">
            <ul class="splide__list items-center w-full">
              <li
                class="splide__slide !w-[650px] max-[1100px]:!w-[75vw] max-[1100px]:max-w-[650px] max-[550px]:!w-[75vw] h-4/5 max-[1100px]:h-full flex justify-center items-center max-[900px]:!w-[100v]"
              >
                <div
                  class="card text-white relative overflow-hidden rounded-[40px] border p-10 border-blue-800 flex flex-col justify-between items-start h-full w-[500px] max-[1100px]:w-[65vw] max-[1100px]:max-w-[500px] max-[550px]:w-[90%]"
                >
                  <video
                    class="absolute h-full top-0 left-0 object-cover"
                    autoplay
                    muted
                    loop
                  >
                    <source src="/video1.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                  </video>
                  <span
                    class="bg-[#04122675] absolute z-10 h-full w-full top-0 left-0 object-cover"
                  ></span>
                  <div
                    class="flex justify-between max-[550px]:justify-center items-start w-full z-20"
                  >
                    <h3
                      class="text-5xl max-[1100px]:text-3xl max-[550px]:text-2xl max-[550px]:w-full"
                    >
                      SOMOS <br /><span class="font-semibold">EMISORES</span>
                    </h3>
                    <span
                      class="font-semibold text-5xl max-[1100px]:text-3xl max-[550px]:text-2xl"
                      >)))</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <p
                    class="text-lg font-semibold w-72 z-20 leading-5 max-[1100px]:text-base max-[550px]:text-sm max-[550px]:w-full"
                  >
                    Desarrollamos <span class="font-extrabold"
                      >soluciones de pago personalizadas</span
                    > para empresas, ajustadas a tus necesidades, respaldadas por
                    un compromiso continuo con la innovación. Simplificamos y potenciamos
                    tus transacciones financieras.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li
                class="splide__slide max-[1100px]:!w-[75vw] max-[1100px]:max-w-[650px] max-[550px]:!w-[75vw] h-4/5 !w-[650px] max-[1100px]:h-full flex justify-center items-center"
              >
                <div
                  class="card text-white relative overflow-hidden rounded-[40px] border p-10 border-blue-800 flex flex-col justify-between items-start h-full w-[500px] max-[1100px]:w-[65vw] max-[1100px]:max-w-[500px] max-[550px]:w-[90%]"
                >
                  <video
                    class="absolute h-full top-0 left-0 object-cover"
                    autoplay
                    muted
                    loop
                  >
                    <source src="/video2.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                  </video>
                  <span
                    class="bg-[#04122675] absolute z-10 w-full h-full top-0 left-0 object-cover"
                  ></span>
                  <div
                    class="flex justify-between max-[550px]:justify-center items-start w-full z-20"
                  >
                    <h3
                      class="text-5xl max-[1100px]:text-3xl max-[550px]:text-2xl max-[550px]:w-full"
                    >
                      SOMOS <br /><span class="font-semibold">PROCESADORES</span
                      >
                    </h3>
                    <span
                      class="font-semibold text-5xl max-[1100px]:text-3xl max-[550px]:text-2xl"
                      >)))</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <p
                    class="text-lg font-semibold w-72 z-20 leading-5 max-[1100px]:text-base max-[550px]:text-sm max-[550px]:w-full"
                  >
                    Administramos <span class="font-extrabold"
                      >transacciones con estándares de seguridad y eficiencia
                      líderes</span
                    > , asegurando la tranquilidad de nuestros clientes. Nuestra
                    máxima prioridad es la dedicación a la protección de tus operaciones
                    financieras.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li
                class="splide__slide !w-[650px] max-[1100px]:!w-[75vw] max-[1100px]:max-w-[650px] max-[550px]:!w-[75vw] h-4/5 max-[1100px]:h-full flex justify-center items-center max-[900px]:!w-[100v]"
              >
                <div
                  class="card text-white relative overflow-hidden rounded-[40px] border p-10 border-blue-800 flex flex-col justify-between items-start h-full w-[500px] max-[1100px]:w-[65vw] max-[1100px]:max-w-[500px] max-[550px]:w-[90%]"
                >
                  <video
                    class="absolute h-full top-0 left-0 object-cover"
                    autoplay
                    muted
                    loop
                  >
                    <source src="/video3.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                  </video>
                  <span
                    class="bg-[#04122675] absolute z-10 w-full h-full top-0 left-0 object-cover"
                  ></span>
                  <div
                    class="flex justify-between max-[550px]:justify-center items-start w-full z-20"
                  >
                    <h3
                      class="text-5xl max-[1100px]:text-3xl max-[550px]:text-2xl max-[550px]:w-full"
                    >
                      SOMOS <br /><span class="font-semibold"
                        >GENERADORES DE PRODUCTOS</span
                      >
                    </h3>
                    <span
                      class="text-5xl max-[500px]:text-3xl max-[550px]:text-2xl"
                      >)))</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <p
                    class="text-lg font-semibold w-72 z-20 leading-5 max-[550px]:text-sm max-[550px]:w-full"
                  >
                    Desarrollamos soluciones de pago personalizadas para
                    empresas, ajustadas a tus necesidades, respaldadas por un
                    compromiso constante con la innovación. Simplificamos y
                    potenciamos tus transacciones financieras.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li
                class="splide__slide !w-[650px] max-[1100px]:!w-[75vw] max-[1100px]:max-w-[650px] max-[550px]:!w-[75vw] h-4/5 max-[1100px]:h-full flex justify-center items-center max-[900px]:!w-[100v]"
              >
                <div
                  class="card text-white relative overflow-hidden rounded-[40px] border p-10 border-blue-800 flex flex-col justify-between items-start h-full w-[500px] max-[1100px]:w-[65vw] max-[1100px]:max-w-[500px] max-[550px]:w-[90%]"
                >
                  <video
                    class="absolute h-full top-0 left-0 object-cover"
                    autoplay
                    muted
                    loop
                  >
                    <source src="/video4.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                  </video>
                  <span
                    class="bg-[#04122675] absolute z-10 w-full h-full top-0 left-0 object-cover"
                  ></span>
                  <div
                    class="flex justify-between max-[550px]:justify-center items-start w-full z-20"
                  >
                    <h3
                      class="text-5xl max-[1100px]:text-3xl max-[550px]:text-2xl max-[550px]:w-full"
                    >
                      SOMOS <br /><span class="font-semibold">CONSULTORES</span>
                    </h3>
                    <span
                      class="text-5xl max-[500px]:text-3xl max-[550px]:text-2xl"
                      >)))</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <p
                    class="text-lg font-semibold w-72 z-20 leading-5 max-[550px]:text-sm max-[550px]:w-full"
                  >
                    Brindamos <span class="font-extrabold"
                      >asesoramiento experto en pagos y finanzas,</span
                    > impulsando el éxito de nuestros clientes. Nuestro compromiso
                    es ser tu socio estratégico en cada paso del camino.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
    <!-- PARTNERSHIP -->
    <section
      class="bg-gradient-to-t to-[#1b2027]  from-[#001228] h-[110vh] max-[1000px]:h-fit max-[1000px]:py-20 max-[700px]:h-full max-[700px]:py-20 flex justify-center items-center flex-col"
    >
      <div class="flex justify-center items-center flex-col h-full">
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-blue-100 w-4/5 font-medium text-lg max-[1366px]:text-base pb-4">
            EN ))) PARTNERSHIP ))) CON
          </h3>
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-2 max-[700px]:grid-cols-1 gap-10 py-20 border-y-2 max-[700px]:border-y-0 border-gray-500 w-4/5"
          >
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center rounded-3xl bg-white w-full max-[700px]:h-[18vh] h-[20vh]"
            >
              <img
                class="w-2/4"
                src="parnership-binance.webp"
                alt="binance logo"
              />
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center rounded-3xl bg-white w-full max-[700px]:h-[18vh] h-[20vh]"
            >
              <img
                class="w-2/4"
                src="\parnership-mastercard.webp"
                alt="mastercard logo"
              />
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center rounded-3xl bg-white w-full max-[700px]:h-[18vh] h-[20vh]"
            >
              <img
                class="w-2/4"
                src="\partnership-plataforma10.webp"
                alt="plataforma10 logo"
              />
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center rounded-3xl bg-white w-full max-[700px]:h-[18vh] h-[20vh]"
            >
              <img
                class="w-2/4"
                src="\partnership-credencial.webp"
                alt="credencial payments logo"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <Contact />
